<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Imgur Gallery</title><link>https://imgur.com</link><description>description</description><lastBuildDate>2022-07-04 13:43:33.382432</lastBuildDate><item><title>Leaving the US.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Gp5HmIA</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tlNSpHW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We started this process 4 years ago through  doing research and saving money. We hired an attorney 18 months back to help us with all paperwork and government forms. They also helped with arranging all the consulate appointments in person. Yes we could have done it without an attorney but frankly, we didn't want to. 

Now everything is finally coming together. Pet passports are in. Queen Mary II tickets are bought. Shipping containers will arrive in 2 months. House has a buyer. Visas just approved. Business loan closed on a new venture we are taking over. New home in under contract. We are doing this. 5 years from now we will be eligible to apply for citizenship. 

We didn't want to tell anyone in case things didn't work out. I didn't want to be like all those other people who simply talked about leaving. But now it's not all talk. We are doing it. We are leaving. And 3 days before my 30th, we will be in Scotland. Good luck to all my fellow Americans. I hope for the best back home but this is not a country I want to spend the rest of my life in anymore. And I need to get my girl out of it before we go full hand maids tale.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Gp5HmIA</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DirtyDusty]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Bell County is in the southeastern part of Kentucky</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/cb0Ayd2</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/W1kdboz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/cb0Ayd2</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[blank666man]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Never forget</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/F7mWL7x</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DV5czh2.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/F7mWL7x</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[malbec]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>They say all strongmen are dumb</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Lq8PqPA</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AjEYwN3.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Lq8PqPA</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mocosoft]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>meanwhile, it cost $75</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/mcS0UaK</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Jfa9Ioq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/mcS0UaK</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[zoraniko]]></dc:c